Issuer: Name of the legal entity issuing the token
IncorporationYear: Year on which the issuer was incorporated
IssuerIsPubliclyTraded: True if the issuer is publicly traded
PublicTradedExchange: Name of the exchange on which the issuer is listed
PublicTradedExchangeTicker: Ticker of the issuer on the exchange on which the issuer is listed
DomiciledIn: Country or jurisdiction in which the issuer is domiciled in
IsEUDomiciled: True if the issuer is domiciled in the EU
CEO.NationalityOrCountryOfBirthOf: Nationality of the CEO; Country of Birth if nationality is unknown
WhitepaperURL: URL at which the whitepaper of the issuer is available at
Licence.Name: Name of the licence the issuer has
Licence.ID: Identifier related to the licence of a regulated actor
Licence.WeblinkToRegulatorService: URL of a service provided by a relevant regulatory authority to check the authenticity of licence information
Regulation.IsEURegulated: True if the issuer is regulated under EU law
